message:
Happy Tuesday everyone!
For those of you who for any reason couldn't make it to the spring break support raising events, you're still in luck! :D Send a completed support letter and a list of 10 addresses of potential supporters to me at ottox339@umn.edu by this Thursday the 18th, and you will receive a $50 scholarship to Big Break or New York.
Attached is a support raising guide, but if you have any more questions or need help writing your support letter, feel free to email/message me or any of the other Fireseeds!
